<p>Transfixed by Dave Underwood's impossible climbing cadence, we three pursuers neglected to watch the pavement below us, and poor Dave Fuller had an unfortunate encounter with a small stone with a mean edge.  Fourmile foiled Fuller, Notheis, and I, but Underwood, Burton, and Raudzens forged onward to conquer the storied canyon walls.  Burton is looking stronger everyday&mdash;rumor has it he's been practicing on weekends too!  Raudzens is a daring descender on her electric blue Townie.  And Underwood is...well...Underwood "The Badger"!!  Until tomorrow!</p>